<item>
            <title>[PIG-3889] Direct fetch doesn&apos;t set job submission timestamps</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-3889</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The following query fails in fetch mode:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
A = load &apos;data&apos; as (a:chararray);   
B = FOREACH A generate &apos;a&apos;, CurrentTime();     
dump B;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Reason: CurrentTime() throws an exception if &lt;tt&gt;pig.job.submitted.timestamp&lt;/tt&gt; is not set.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
